widgets.TITLE: Dashboards: Active
widgets.TITLE_INFO: Total number of active dashboards.

JSON_SETTINGS.query:
| source appdb
	query=`
SELECT COUNT(*) AS COUNT 
FROM CFW_DASHBOARD
WHERE IS_ARCHIVED IS NOT TRUE
   AND VERSION = 0
	`
| formatfield 
	COUNT = [ ['align', "center"], ['css', "font-weight", "bold"] ]
| display 
	as=title 
	titlefields=[COUNT]
	menu=false
	zoom=300

widgets.TITLE: Members In Roles
widgets.TITLE_INFO: Number of users which are part of the specified role.

JSON_SETTINGS.query:
| source appdb
	query=`
SELECT G.NAME, COUNT(*) AS COUNT FROM CFW_ROLE G 
JOIN CFW_USER_ROLE_MAP M 
ON M.FK_ID_ROLE = G.PK_ID 
WHERE G.IS_GROUP=FALSE
GROUP BY G.NAME
ORDER BY NAME
	`
| display menu=false

widgets.TITLE: Dashboards Created
widgets.TITLE_INFO: Number of newly created dashboards.

JSON_SETTINGS.query:
| source appdb 
	query=`
SELECT TIME_CREATED
FROM CFW_DASHBOARD
WHERE IS_ARCHIVED IS NOT TRUE
   AND VERSION = 0
   AND TIME_CREATED >= DATEADD(MS, `+earliest()+`, DATE '1970-01-01') 
   AND TIME_CREATED <= DATEADD(MS, `+latest()+`, DATE '1970-01-01')
	`
| crates
	by=TIME_CREATED # use values of the field 'TIME'
	type=time # evaluate time in epoch milliseconds
	step= interval()
	timeunit=intervalunit() # minutes, so rounds to 5 minutes
| stats
	by=[CRATE]
	COUNT=count()
| chart
	type=bar
	x=CRATE
	y=COUNT
	showlegend=false
